      <p class="resultText">Based on your responses, we have identified that <span class="font-weight-bold" cuticle_reasons>environmental factors, chemical treatments <span class="font-weight-normal">and</span> usage of styling tools</span> are top reasons behind your <span class="font-weight-bold" cuticle_causes>dull, dry, frizzy hair, split ends, hair breakage and tangling</span> concerns.</p>
      <p class="resultText mb-3">But don't worry, we have the perfect hair care routine to address all your concerns.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="product-area">
      <p class="font-weight-bold routine mb-0 pb-2 pb-md-3">Your Customized Hair Routine :</p>
      <div class="row pt-md-4 justify-content-center" cuticle_products>
        
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="button_shadow mb-4">
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between cuticle__button_container align-items-center py-2">
      <div>
        <p class="m-0 ttl_cart_value pb-md-1 pb-2">Total</p>
        <p class="font-weight-bold m-0 cart__price pb-md-1 pb-2"><sup>â‚¹</sup><span cart_value>300</span> /-</p>
        <p class="incl_tax m-0">Inclusive of all taxes</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="female_buy_price_wd">
        <p id="add-to-cart-result-page-frp" class="btn new-female-buynowATC">
          <span class="mr-2"><img src="//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0100/1622/7394/files/dddd.png" width="" height="" loading="eager" title="Buy Now" alt="Buy Now"></span>BUY NOW
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
  {
    "name": "Cuticle Banner",
    "tag": "section",
    "class": "section",
    "settings": [
      {
        "type": "color",
        "id": "backgroud_color",
        "label": "Select Background Color",
        "default": "#fff"
      }
    ],
    "presets": [
      {
        "name": "Cuticle Banner",
        "category": "slideshow"
      }
    ]
  }
{% endschema %}

{% style %}
  .cuticle__button_container {
    padding: 0 9rem;
  }
  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .cuticle-banner {
    margin-top: 45px;
    padding: 30px 9rem 0;
    background: {{ section.settings.backgroud_color }};
  }
  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .username {
    font-size: 25px;
    line-height: 32.74px;
  }
  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .resultText {
    font-size: 24px;
    line-height: 32.74px;
  }
  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .routine {
    font-size: 24px;
    line-height: 26.88px;
  }
  .cuticle__buyBTN {
    font-size: 21.85px;
    line-height: 29.81px;
    min-width: 300px;
    background: #B7D340;
    border: 1px solid #B7D340;
    border-radius: 30px;
    color: #414042;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .cuticle_pd_name {
    font-size: 24px;
    line-height: 26.88px;
  }
  .cuticle_pd_uses {
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 22.4px;
  }
  .cuticle_pd_uses::marker {
    color: #9E83D7;
  }
  .cuticle__product__price, .cuticle_product_prices {
    font-size: 32px;
    line-height: 35.84px;
  }
  .product__size {
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 22.4px;
  }
  li.cuticle_pd_uses {
    list-style: inherit;
  }
  [cuticle_products] .slick-prev {
    left: -15px;
    top: 50%;
    background: #EEEAFB;
    padding: 5px;
    height: 35px;
    width: 35px!important;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  [cuticle_products] .slick-prev:before {
    content: "";
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-top: 2px solid #000;
    border-right: 2px solid #000;
    display: block;
    transform: rotate(-135deg);
    margin: auto;
  }
  [cuticle_products] .slick-next:before {
    content: "";
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-top: 2px solid #000;
    border-right: 2px solid #000;
    display: block;
    transform: rotate(45deg);
    margin: auto;
  }
  [cuticle_products] .slick-next {
    right: 0;
    top: 50%;
    background: #EEEAFB;
    padding: 5px;
    height: 35px;
    width: 35px!important;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .incl_tax {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 19.1px;
    color: #41404280;
  }
  .ttl_cart_value {
    font-size: 24px;
    line-height: 32.74px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .cart__price {
    font-size: 36px;
    line-height: 40.32px;
    color: #3E3E3E;
  }
  .button_shadow {
    box-shadow: 0px 4.565333366394043px 4.565333366394043px 0px #00000040;
  }
  [btn_sticky] {
    width: 100%;
    background: #fff;
    bottom: 0;
    z-index: 9;
  }
  .cuticle_sticky_btn {
    width: 100%;
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 0;
    z-index: 98;
  }
  .cuticle__buyBTN:hover {
    background: #000;
    border-color: #000;
    color: #fff;
  }
  .cuticle__buyBTN:hover img {
    filter: brightness(0) invert(1);
  }
  .cuticle__product__price:before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 100%;
    width: 2px;
    background: #9E83D7;
    border-radius: 30px;
  }
  @media only screen and (max-width: 1199.98px) and (min-width: 768px) {
    .cuticle__button_container {
      padding: 0 60px;
    }
    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .cuticle-banner {
      padding: 30px 60px 0;
    }
    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .resultText {
      font-size: 20px;
      line-height: 26.74px;
    }
    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .routine {
      font-size: 20px;
      line-height: 24.88px
    }
    .cuticle_pd_name {
      font-size: 22px;
      line-height: 24.88px;
    }
    .cuticle_pd_uses {
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 20.4px;
    }
    .cuticle__product__price, .cuticle_product_prices {
      font-size: 25px;
      line-height: 30.84px;
    }
    .product__size {
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 18.4px;
    }
  }
  @media only screen and (max-width: 767.98px) and (min-width: 576px) {
    .cuticle__button_container {
      padding: 0 30px;
    }
    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .cuticle-banner {
      margin-top: 40px;
      padding: 30px 30px 0;
    }
    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .username {
      line-height: 24.36px;
    }
    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .resultText {
      font-size: 18.98px;
      line-height: 26.74px;
    }
    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .routine {
      font-size: 20px;
      line-height: 24.88px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .cuticle__buyBTN {
      font-size: 15.84px;
      line-height: 21.6px;
      min-width: unset;
      width: 50%;
    }
  }
  @media only screen and (max-width: 575.98px) {
    .cuticle__button_container {
      padding: 0 30px;
    }
    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .cuticle-banner {
      margin-top: 40px;
      padding: 30px 30px 0;
    }
    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .username {
      line-height: 24.36px;
    }
    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .resultText {
      font-size: 15.98px;
      line-height: 24.36px;
    }
    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .routine {
      font-size: 18.28px;
      line-height: 20.47px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .cuticle__buyBTN {
      font-size: 15.84px;
      line-height: 21.6px;
      min-width: unset;
      width: 50%;
    }
  }
  @media only screen and (max-width: 767.98px) {
    [cuticle_products]:not(.slick-initialized) > [product_card]:first-of-type ~ * {
      display: none;
    }
    .cuticle_pd_name {
      font-size: 18.28px;
      line-height: 20.47px;
    }
    .cuticle_pd_uses {
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 15.68px;
    }
    .cuticle__product__price, .cuticle_product_prices {
      font-size: 22.22px;
      line-height: 24.89px;
    }
    .product__size {
      font-size: 16.67px;
      line-height: 18.67px;
    }
    .ttl_cart_value {
      font-size: 14.8px;
      line-height: 20.18px;
    }
    .cart__price {
      font-size: 26.67px;
      line-height: 29.87px;
    }
    .cuticle__product__price:before {
      width: 1px;
    }
  }
  @media only screen and (max-width: 400px) {
    .cuticle__product__price, .cuticle_product_prices {
      font-size: 20.22px;
      line-height: 24.89px;
    }
    .product__size {
      font-size: 14.67px;
      line-height: 18.67px;
    }
    .cart__price {
      font-size: 22.67px;
      padding-bottom: 0!important;
    }
    .incl_tax {
      font-size: 11px;
    }
    .cuticle__button_container {
      padding: 0 14px 10px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}